column-content\">\n\n                    <div class=\"item\">\n                        <span class=\"product-name\">Claude Code</span>\n                        <div class=\"item-title\">\n                            <a href=\"https://github.com/anthropics/claude-code/releases/tag/v2.1.63\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                                Version 2.1.63 - Multiple slash commands and memory improvements\n                            </a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"item-description\">\n                            Added /simplify and /batch bundled slash commands, HTTP hooks for external integrations, and extensive memory leak fixes across the platform (20+ fixes).\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"item-meta\">\n                            <span class=\"update-type release\">Release</span>\n                            <a href=\"https://github.com/anthropics/claude-code/releases/tag/v2.1.63\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Release Notes</a>\n                            | 2026-02-28\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"item\">\n                        <span class=\"product-name\">Continue</span>\n                        <div class=\"item-title\">\n                            <a href=\"https://github.com/continuedev/continue/releases\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                                Version 1.3.32 - MCP App support and cn checks\n                            </a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"item-description\">\n                            Added limited MCP App support, cn checks CLI command, enabled agent mode for LM Studio models, updated default model to Claude Opus 4.6, and consolidated React best practices.\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"item-meta\">\n                            <span class=\"update-type feature\">Feature</span>\n                            <a href=\"https://github.com/continuedev/continue/releases\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Release Notes</a>\n                            | 2026-02-27\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"item\">\n                        <span class=\"product-name\">Cursor</span>\n                        <div class=\"item-title\">\n                            <a href=\"https://cursor.com/changelog\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                                Bugbot Autofix with Cloud Agents\n                            </a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"item-description\">\n                            Bugbot can automatically fix issues it finds in pull requests using cloud agents that run in isolated VMs with full development environments. Over 35% of autofix changes are merged into base PRs. Resolution rate increased from 52% to 76%.\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"item-meta\">\n                            <span class=\"update-type feature\">Feature</span>\n                            <a href=\"https://cursor.com/changelog\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Changelog</a>\n                            | 2026-02-26\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"community-feedback\">\n                            <div class=\"feedback-item\">\"Can significantly improve efficiency - You submit a PR, wake up the next morning, and Bugbot has already fixed 10 small issues\" <span class=\"feedback-source\">— 51CTO <span class=\"sentiment-positive\">↑</span></span></div>\n                            <div class=\"feedback-item\">\"Over-reliance might cause developers to lose code understanding. Risk of blindly accepting fixes without reviewing\" <span class=\"feedback-source\">— 51CTO <span class=\"sentiment-neutral\">→</span></span></div>\n                        </div>\n 