iguration for LSP servers, WorktreeCreate and WorktreeRemove hook events. Fixed critical bugs: resumed sessions visibility with symlinks, session data loss on SSH disconnect, and memory leaks.\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"item-meta\">\n                            <span class=\"update-type release\">Release</span>\n                            <a href=\"https://github.com/anthropics/claude-code/releases/tag/v2.1.50\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Release Notes</a>\n                            | 2026-02-20\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"item\">\n                        <span class=\"product-name\">Claude Code</span>\n                        <div class=\"item-title\">\n                            <a href=\"https://www.anthropic.com/engineering/building-c-compiler\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                                Building a C Compiler with Agent Teams\n                            </a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"item-description\">\n                            Anthropic engineer Nicholas Carlini developed 'agent teams' - multiple Claude Code instances working in parallel on a shared codebase. Over 2,000 sessions and $20,000 in API costs, 16 agents produced a 100,000-line Rust-based C compiler.\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"item-meta\">\n                            <span class=\"update-type announcement\">Announcement</span>\n                            <a href=\"https://www.anthropic.com/engineering/building-c-compiler\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Read More</a>\n                            | 2026-02-16\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"item\">\n                        <span class=\"product-name\">Devin</span>\n                        <div class=\"item-title\">\n                            <a 